{
  "chapter": 50,
  "chapter_summary": "本章为\"同盟异梦\"，围绕裴珏被推举为江南同盟盟主后所面临的重重危机展开。金鸡帮帮主向一啼在众目睽睽之下公然反对裴珏，却遭到同伙\"七巧追魂\"那飞虹的暗算身亡——那飞虹以\"清理门户\"为名除去异己，实则野心勃勃。东方兄弟因受人挑拨与那飞虹对峙，却被其巧言令色化解。那飞虹为裴珏安排城郊落脚之处，言语间不断试探其与檀明的仇恨。随后金鸡帮残众方家兄弟率众射箭行刺，裴珏挺身而出以身挡箭，其仁义之举令金鸡帮众深受感化，纷纷归降。冷谷双木在旁观察局势，对那飞虹的城府深感忧虑。本章展现了裴珏以德服人的领袖魅力，以及江湖中各方势力的明争暗斗。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_han_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "冷寒竹",
      "listener": "char_leng_ku_mu",
      "text": "我们不如替玱儿将这厮解决了吧！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_ku_mu",
      "speaker_name": "冷枯木",
      "listener": "char_leng_han_zhu",
      "text": "不如让他将此人收服，将来也好做他的一条臂膀。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "众人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那飞虹怎的来了！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_han_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "冷寒竹",
      "listener": "char_leng_ku_mu",
      "text": "若是此人有出手之意……",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_ku_mu",
      "speaker_name": "冷枯木",
      "listener": "char_leng_han_zhu",
      "text": "我怎能容他出手？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_yi_ti",
      "speaker_name": "金鸡·向一啼",
      "listener": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "text": "那大哥，你来了么，好极好极，这种暴发的小人，怎能容他当‘江南同盟’的盟主，还是快些将他除去算了！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "七巧追魂·那飞虹",
      "listener": "char_xiang_yi_ti",
      "text": "你不愿‘裴大先生’做‘江南同盟’的盟主是么？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 43,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_yi_ti",
      "speaker_name": "金鸡·向一啼",
      "listener": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "text": "正是，他不配。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "七巧追魂·那飞虹",
      "listener": "char_xiang_yi_ti",
      "text": "好极，好极。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_ku_mu",
      "speaker_name": "冷枯木",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "留心暗器！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_yi_ti",
      "speaker_name": "金鸡·向一啼",
      "listener": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "text": "你……你……你……狠……",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "七巧追魂·那飞虹",
      "listener": "char_xiang_yi_ti",
      "text": "不守帮规，反叛盟主，罪不容诬，你还在这里想什么？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 65,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "七巧追魂·那飞虹",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "盟主你可受惊了么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴玱",
      "listener": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "text": "你……你这是……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "七巧追魂·那飞虹",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "叛帮与叛师同罪，江湖上人人得而诫之，盟主你虽然存心仁厚，但在下却不能让这种以下犯上的万恶之徒逍遥法外。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴玱",
      "listener": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "text": "但你又何苦如此心急。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_han_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "冷寒竹",
      "listener": "char_leng_ku_mu",
      "text": "这‘七巧追魂’果然是他约好的帮手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "七巧追魂·那飞虹",
      "listener": "char_dong_fang_jiang",
      "text": "我当是谁？原来是两位东方少侠，却不知两位何时学会了在暗中伤人的本领？倒教在下服得很。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 105,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang_jiang",
      "speaker_name": "东方江",
      "listener": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "text": "我如此对待惯于暗中伤人之辈，还真客气得很；否则你此刻还能与我兄弟两人说话么？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 113,
      "line_end": 115
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "七巧追魂·那飞虹",
      "listener": "char_dong_fang_jiang",
      "text": "如此说来，我倒要感激两位才是了！",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang_hu",
      "speaker_name": "东方湖",
      "listener": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "text": "少在少爷面前逜一时口舌之利，你唆使手下，散发狂言，若不赶紧说个清楚，我立时便要你伤在剑下，可没有方才那般客气了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 123,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "七巧追魂·那飞虹",
      "listener": "char_dong_fang_hu",
      "text": "什么事？这倒教在下不懂了。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 129,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang_jiang",
      "speaker_name": "东方江",
      "listener": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "text": "你手下已在众目所视之下招认了，你难道还想狡赚么？我倒要问问你，方才那些在暗中辱骂我兄弟的人，莫非不是你的手下？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 133,
      "line_end": 137
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "七巧追魂·那飞虹",
      "listener": "char_dong_fang_jiang",
      "text": "不错，那些人都是我的手下，是我在暗中指使他们！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 141,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang_jiang",
      "speaker_name": "东方江",
      "listener": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "text": "既然是你主使，你或是在我兄弟面前跬下认错，或是拔出兵刃，与我兄弟一决生死！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "七巧追魂·那飞虹",
      "listener": "char_dong_fang_jiang",
      "text": "那般人到哪里去了，莫非都已死在贤昆仲的剑下？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 151,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang_jiang",
      "speaker_name": "东方江",
      "listener": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "text": "他们俱是受命于你，自然怪不了他们！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "七巧追魂·那飞虹",
      "listener": "char_dong_fang_jiang",
      "text": "但我亦是受命于人，岂能怪得了我？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang_jiang",
      "speaker_name": "东方江",
      "listener": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "text": "谁？指使你的是谁？莫非是‘神手’战飞，抒是……",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "七巧追魂·那飞虹",
      "listener": "char_dong_fang_jiang",
      "text": "指使我的人不是别人，便是令尊东方老堡主！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 165,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang_jiang",
      "speaker_name": "东方江",
      "listener": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "text": "好个大胆的狂徒，居然敢来捉弄我兄弟，快些拔剑受死！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "七巧追魂·那飞虹",
      "listener": "char_dong_fang_jiang",
      "text": "别人口中的话，两位深信不疑，在下口中的话，两位为何就不相信了呢？这倒怪了！",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "七巧追魂·那飞虹",
      "listener": "char_dong_fang_jiang",
      "text": "片面之词，两位怎能深信？我那飞虹岂是那种人物？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_han_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "冷寒竹",
      "listener": "char_leng_ku_mu",
      "text": "好个侠嘴侠口的老江湖！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_ku_mu",
      "speaker_name": "冷枯木",
      "listener": "char_leng_han_zhu",
      "text": "这种人成事不足，败事却有余，最难想了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "七巧追魂·那飞虹",
      "listener": "char_dong_fang_hu",
      "text": "两位少侠以后若要审问犯人，不妨来通知在下一声。",
      "tone": "调促",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "七巧追魂·那飞虹",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "盟主在这里可有落脚之处，还是即刻就要动身！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴玱",
      "listener": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "text": "我准备随意寻家客栈。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "七巧追魂·那飞虹",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "此刻不但汉口城中家家客栈俱已无法插足，便是汉阳镇里，也没有一家客栈可以容身了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴玱",
      "listener": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "text": "那么……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "七巧追魂·那飞虹",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "在下在城郊附近，倒有一处空屋，不知盟主可否屈驾，反此只不过是数天的时日，一切事都能解决了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 211,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴玱",
      "listener": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "text": "那是最好，不过……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "飞龙镞局骑士",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "檀总镞头有令，‘飞龙旗’下所属的所有兄弟们，立刻检点行装，随时随地，待命而发！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 231
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "七巧追魂·那飞虹",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "盟主，你可知道战神手到哪里去了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴玱",
      "listener": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "text": "战兄只怕已返江南，因他算定了檀明必是要对他家宅不利，再来也是在江南布置一下，专等‘飞龙镞局’的镮车渡江南下。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "七巧追魂·那飞虹",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "近来江湖传言，说是盟主与檀明怀有不共戴天之仇，不知盟主如何打算，可有要小弟效劳之处？",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 249,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴玱",
      "listener": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "text": "檀明可是也要到这里来么？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "七巧追魂·那飞虹",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "想必如此！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴玱",
      "listener": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "text": "这就是我为什么留在此地的缘由了。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "七巧追魂·那飞虹",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "那么……盟主，你与冷氏兄弟的赌约……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 263,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴玱",
      "listener": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "text": "事已至此，胜负全已无妨，普天之下，还有比父叔之仇更重要的事么？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 269
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "七巧追魂·那飞虹",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "无论如何，让小弟带盟主到那落脚之处去才是！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "江南同盟众汉子",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "小的俱是‘江南同盟’中人，只是身份悬殊，是以一直不敢与盟主说话，但盟主在此地无落脚之处，小的倒可将住的客栈先让出来。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 279
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "七巧追魂·那飞虹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不用了，在下已为盟主大哥准备了宿处。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴玱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "多谢各位的关心，我……我实在感激得很。",
      "tone": "感动",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_leng_han_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "冷寒竹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "闪开！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_na_fei_hong",
      "speaker_name": "七巧追魂·那飞虹",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "这些都是‘金鸡帮‟众，穿身碧衣的两人，便是向一啼手下的大将，‘鸡目’方家兄弟！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 327,
      "line_end": 329
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴玱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们这是为了什么？即使与我有仇，又何苦伤及他人！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 323,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴玱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们原来是为了替帮主复仇，我不怪你，今日你们虽然功败垂成，但……唉，你们快去吧，以后总会有复仇的机会。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 333,
      "line_end": 335
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_yi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "鸡目·方一奇",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "小人们不知裴大先生竟然如此仁义慰慨，是以才做出这等事情！此刻但凭盟主你责罚，小的倒没有半句怨言。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 341,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_yi_ou",
      "speaker_name": "鸡目·方一偶",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "盟主如此仁义，小人们以后怎敢再有反叛之心？今日受这责罚，纵然盟主不愿，小人倒也要跟在盟主身后，为盟主效劳。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 347,
      "line_end": 349
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴玱",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既然如此，各位就请快些起来，雪地严寒，各位休要冻坏了身体。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 50,
      "line_start": 353,
      "line_end": 355
    }
